  <br/>
  Clcr = {(140 - age ) X weight[kg] )} / (sCr [umol/L] X 0.8)           if female X 0.85
  <br/>
Clcr = {(140 - <%=age%> ) X <%=weight%>[kg] )} / (sCr [umol/L] X 0.8)   <% if(female){%> X 0.85 <%}%>
  -->
